# .mantaignore — Suppress specific Manta findings
#
# Format: [file-glob]  [keyword-or-severity]  # optional reason
#
# Examples:
#   src/utils/hash.ts  MD5                    # non-security use of MD5
#   src/generated/**   DRY                    # generated code — DRY not applicable
#   **                 INFO                   # suppress all INFO findings globally
#
# Severities: CRITICAL, WARNING, INFO
# Suppressions are applied by all review orchestrators before reporting.
# Use for intentional trade-offs, accepted risk, or false positives — not to hide real issues.
